{"tid":1645834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武-和理非方程式以中斷","createTime":"2019-10-11T04:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T11:05:56.000Z","uid":303297,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2ddf0c501027a969648388036d571d6c62793a","tid":1645834,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"大家好似唔記得左和理非的作用<br />\n和理非示威（人鏈，唱歌）反抗性質其實好低，似一種象徵性活動，作用係去受權勇武，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從來勇武係主動，和理非係被動</span></span><br />\n但係依家反而變左和理非為主導，開個花又話休息等美國，裝個修又話對方有幾成係外資<br />\n我明白最近和理非文宣的確開左唔少路（NBA South Park Blizzard)但希望大家唔好太沉醉係國際戰線，而去限制勇武<br />\n我地每休息一下，黑警就多一段時間上查勇武真正身份，我地每休息一下，就多個勇武比人查家宅<br />\n真心，依家浮屍身份又出，性侵受害人又出，根本就已經係名正言順有開花的理由，以前我地成日問勇武幾時可以進化，去用魔法etc.今日我問返句和理非又幾時可以進化呢？<br />\n我希望大家休息時唔好失去抗爭的信念"},{"pid":"0ee1c5744ba684abcae6c0521ac613aa1d5ffa79","tid":1645834,"uid":322429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e407d59815c2828a0df86c4443aaa684bfad8cf","tid":1645834,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee1c5744ba684abcae6c0521ac613aa1d5ffa79","tid":1645834,"uid":322429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"P牌推乜嘢<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c777d65140af37c4e89507b7207680ecb6b32a4","tid":1645834,"uid":209910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"680fb370ae5ffe75eb589fc08d8ad6410f427665","tid":1645834,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor